# Issue 003: Download and Analyze Source Code

## Current Behavior
No local copy of the City of Heroes server source code exists in the project.

## Intended Behavior
Have the complete City of Heroes server source code downloaded locally with initial analysis of the codebase structure and build requirements.

## Suggested Implementation Steps
1. Clone or download the identified source code repository
2. Organize source code in the src/ directory structure
3. Analyze the project structure and identify main components
4. Read any existing documentation or README files
5. Identify build scripts and compilation instructions
6. Create initial codebase analysis documentation
7. List all external dependencies and requirements

